title: No. 4 Tech clinches series sweep with walk-off blast - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 4 Tech clinches series sweep with walk-off blast - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The No. 4 Texas Tech baseball team rallied on Sunday, scoring three runs in the bottom of the ninth, to defeat Kansas State 7-6 at Rip Griffin Park. Sophomore sensation Jace Jung provided the walk-off home run (watch) to seal the comeback bid that clinched a series sweep.
